description: A Cut Above is serving authentic German street cuisine right in the heart of Columbus, and it’s all just so über tasty. From grilled Bratwurst on a pretzel stick, to Schnitzel Sandwiches with pork or chicken and succulent secret sauce on a kaiser bun, to big juicy Frankfurters, you get to enjoy the greatest flavors from Germany without even having to grab your passport. For all this and more, come by this truck and order up some Deutschland deliciousness!
name: A Cut Above - Schnitzel & More
